text: :St. Stephen's Cathedral, Vienna is also called Stephansdom St. Stephan's Cathedral is a baroque Cathedral. It was finished in 1688 in Passau, Germany. It is the seat of the Catholic Bishop of Passau and the main church of his diocese.
